{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ARjbV2KJBjRTtbDRuqRFSc","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Sidebar.tsx Analysis\n\n**File Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/components/Sidebar.tsx`\n\n### Full Component Structure\n\nThe Sidebar is a collapsible left navigation panel with three main sections:\n\n1. **The Pit** (Games section) - 5 game links\n2. **Player** (User features) - Profile, Loot Crates, Quests\n3. **Platform** - Provably Fair\n\n### NavLink Pattern\n\nEach NavLink follows this structure:\n\n```tsx\n<NavLink to=\"/route\" className={({ isActive }) => `nv-item ${isActive ? \"active\" : \"\"}`} style={{ \"--nc\": \"var(--color-XXX)\" } as React.CSSProperties}>\n  <div className=\"nv-ico\">\n    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 17 17\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" ...>\n      {/* SVG path/element content */}\n    </svg>\n  </div>\n  <span className=\"nv-lbl\">Label Text</span>\n  {/* Optional badge */}\n  {condition && <span className=\"nv-bdg color-class\">{count}</span>}\n</NavLink>\n```\n\n### \"Player\" Section Details (Lines 123-161)\n\nThe Player section contains three items:\n\n1. **Profile** (`/profile`)\n   - Color: `--color-blue` (#3D7FFF)\n   - Icon: Person silhouette (circle head + shoulders path)\n\n2. **Loot Crates** (`/loot`)\n   - Color: `--color-yellow` (#FFB800)\n   - Icon: Treasure chest (rect + lid + keyhole)\n   - Badge: `unopenedChestCount > 0` â†’ `nv-bdg yl` (yellow badge)\n\n3. **Quests** (`/quests`) â€” Lines 151-160\n   - Color: `--color-green` (#00E676)\n   - Icon: Circle with checkmark (circle + polyline points=\"5.5,8.5 7.2,10.5 11.5,6\")\n   - Badge: `claimableQuestCount > 0` â†’ `nv-bdg pk` (pink badge)\n\n### SVG Icon Pattern\n\nAll SVG icons use:\n- `viewBox=\"0 0 17 17\"` (standardized 17Ă—17 canvas)\n- `fill=\"none\"` (stroke only)\n- `stroke=\"currentColor\"` (inherits text color, which is set via `--nc` CSS variable)\n- `strokeWidth=\"1.5\"` or `1.4` (consistent line weights)\n- `strokeLinecap=\"round\"` and `strokeLinejoin=\"round\"` (optional, for smooth corners)\n\n### Color Variables Used in Sidebar\n\n| Section | NavLink | Color Variable | Hex Value |\n|---------|---------|---|---|\n| The Pit | All Games | `--color-pink` | #FF1F8E |\n| The Pit | Flip You | `--color-yellow` | #FFB800 |\n| The Pit | Jackpot | `--color-pink` | #FF1F8E |\n| The Pit | Close Call | `--color-green` | #00E676 |\n| The Pit | Crypto Crash | `--color-red` | #FF2D55 |\n| The Pit | Game of Trades | `--color-blue` | #3D7FFF |\n| Player | Profile | `--color-blue` | #3D7FFF |\n| Player | Loot Crates | `--color-yellow` | #FFB800 |\n| Player | **Quests** | **`--color-green`** | **#00E676** |\n| Platform | Provably Fair | `--color-muted2` | #5C5C7A |\n\n### CSS Classes for Styling\n\n- `.nv-item` â€” nav link container (active state handled via `isActive`)\n- `.nv-ico` â€” icon wrapper (22px Ă— 22px, contains 17Ă—17 SVG)\n- `.nv-lbl` â€” label text\n- `.nv-bdg` â€” badge (notification count)\n  - `.nv-bdg.gr` (gray)\n  - `.nv-bdg.yl` (yellow)\n  - `.nv-bdg.pk` (pink)\n\n### Key Hooks Used\n\n- `useWallet()` â€” wallet connection state\n- `useQuests()` â€” returns `{ unopenedChestCount, claimableQuestCount }` (used for badges)\n\n---\n\nThis gives you the complete reference for the Sidebar structure, the exact \"Quests\" location in the Player section (lines 151-160), the SVG icon pattern, and all color assignments."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aa7700646eb483f64 (use SendMessage with to: 'aa7700646eb483f64' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 42498\ntool_uses: 5\nduration_ms: 33632</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4718ef4b-5b78-4595-bd86-4abb58e68966","uuid":"192409e8-60eb-4774-b703-3ec65800c831","timestamp":"2026-03-25T13:07:24.840Z","tool_use_result":{"status